data.description: Tastefully updated 3-2 sitting on an expansive 1.7-acre lot! Get away to your private country getaway, all the while enjoying convenient access US-75 that gives you an easy drive to work, shopping, dining, entertainment, and much more! The home's open and inviting floor plan is perfect for hosting those closest to you. Brilliantly remodeled kitchen comes with stylish two-tone cabinetry, a spacious island, sleek granite countertops, modern fixtures, and stainless steel appliances. Luxury vinyl plank flooring runs throughout the common areas, giving you durable flooring that is built to last and adding rustic character to the home. The updated bathroom comes complete with new vanity, updated fixtures, and tiled walk-in rain shower. A portion of the lot has been fenced to give you a cozy, tree-shaded backyard with a covered patio, where you can enjoy the scenic views! Huge detached garage offers a perfect space for a workshop, and a sizeable shed offers plenty of extra storage space.
